1. Introduced new method to String class (isBlank, lines, strip, stripLeading, SpripTrailing, repeat)
  1.1 isBlank = It's advanced version of isEmpty() by checking,  s (space) and the \t, \n, \r, and \f escape sequences
  1.2 lines = Convert string to list of string if there is any \n present.
  1.3 strip = remove leading and trailing spaces from string, it's higher version of trim(). trim() only supports 
              200 Unicode but this support all Unicode.
  1.4 repeat = It will return concanating of the same string with N'th time.

2. It's become easier to read and write string from file.
   2.1 They have introduced new static method like readString, writeString from Files.class

3. 
